Pre-requisites:
- Harbour 2.0.0 or later
- Windows, Linux or Darwin (Mac OS X)

Build:
# cd src
# hbmk2 modelo8.hbp
# ./modelo8

Tested on:
Windows, intel P4 32 bit, mingw and Visual C++ 2008 Express
Linux (Ubuntu 10.4), intel P4 32 bit, gcc 4.??
Mac OS X, 32bit G4, gcc 4.?? (XCode 3)

Please note that Mac OS X must have X11 installed.
